hopobject.body: I'm self-employed compound care plus pharmacy loxley al It may seem bizarre that a man who has lived such a life can come up with nothing interesting to say about it, although his caginess fits securely into the pattern of self-protection that has kept Jagger afloat throughout his professional life. Such public pronouncements as he makes are reliably anodyne, and as Philip Norman – the most recent biographer to take him on as a subject notes – it is almost impossible to find an interview in which Mick has disclosed anything of real interest about himself.
